short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays a rating bar (likes/dislikes) on the bottom of every YouTube™ video thumbnail.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is open source on GitHub. If you find any bugs or have any suggestions, please open an issue here: https://github.com/elliotwaite/thumbnail-rating-bar-for-youtube
